item.title: Maps of office rents in France by metro station
item.description: For the 10st consecutive year, Cushman & Wakefield publishes its maps of rental values for office space by metro station in Paris, Lyon and Marseille. For each metro station, these values correspond to the average rental values for offices >100 sqm available immediately and in 2025. These values exclude charges and taxes and are weighted by surface area.
